{"tid":984633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9個同事夾錢買彩票中3.5億頭獎 集體辭職癱瘓公司生產線","createTime":"2019-01-17T03:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T12:46:19.000Z","uid":54373,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1fce353e4fda4c14e1d195d157ecd84ecaec6fa8","tid":984633,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:13:41.000Z","msg":"作為打工仔，有咩開心得過中六合彩，然後裸辭唔使再打工受氣？就係成班同事都一齊中獎，然後一齊裸辭「劈炮唔撈」！大家一齊起腳飛起間公司！加拿大安大略省就有9個汽車零件工人夾份買彩票後中頭獎，累積獎金高達6000萬加幣（約3.5億港元），中獎後，9個工人集體辭職！Wow！齋聽都興奮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/20190115h012_18168109085c3da457925b5-800x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F20190115h012_18168109085c3da457925b5-800x480.jpg&h=199c6b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據CTV News報道，加拿大安大略省一家汽車零部件製造商的9個汽車零件工人，夾份買彩票幸運地中頭獎，贏得累積獎金高達6000萬加幣（約3.5億港元）後，9個同事集體辭職。<br />\n<br />\n9個年齡介乎21至57歲的同事，在一間名為Guelph&rsquo;s Linamar Corporation的汽車零件公司一起工作，感情要好。<br />\n<br />\n組長Ala Hirmiz指：「我們總是聊天、開玩笑，慶祝彼此的生日。現在我們一起慶祝這場令人難以置信的勝利！」<br />\n<br />\n其中一個同事說，過去幾個月，他們開始買彩票，他們只會下注50美元以上的彩票，因為他們想要贏大的、不想要小的。<br />\n<br />\n在中頭獎前，他們只買過3到4次彩票。<br />\n<br />\n同事中Mussie Kelete和Ella Nicole Cabrera在他們贏得的那一周才第一次夾份下注。<br />\n<br />\n開彩後，最初Meneses認為他們只贏了6000美元，但再次掃描了票，發現他們贏得了大獎。<br />\n<br />\n直至先後核實了第7次，他們才真正知道自己中了頭獎！<br />\n<br />\n中獎後，9個同事決定集體辭職，表示雖然離開並不容易，但這次中獎讓他們有機會尋求夢想。<br />\n<br />\n員工中獎可以唔使再打工固然高興，但該公司的主管就非常不滿，因為他們集體辭職，癱瘓了整條生產線。<br />\n<br />\n9個員工表示，即使他們不再每天都能看到對方，他們仍然會保持聯繫，計劃從現在起一年的聚會，並通過電話和短信保持聯絡。"},{"pid":"91b088b7426ba0b974d7adc9e7fa17590fa643f0","tid":984633,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"俾你中左3.5億 係咪第一時間買兇毆跛雞姦朗對腳?"},{"pid":"33f3e9699451a37b57ca76d785111595d065d6e1","tid":984633,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"91b088b7426ba0b974d7adc9e7fa17590fa643f0","tid":984633,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"俾你中左3.5億 係咪第一時間買兇毆跛雞姦朗對腳?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"唔會,佢咁垃圾,生存到只係靠寫手吹大<br />\n<br />\n去南洋搵個法師落佢降頭巫術就可能會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b269b472951547d80984bf4f9e5a1adbf796ff1d","tid":984633,"uid":11977,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"主管： 屌你老母唔預埋我"},{"pid":"06a57bbc22fbb718672ce33482638b0a54af2f65","tid":984633,"uid":39381,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"主管人緣差 夾錢冇佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71db95a6962193b3f103fa12953415e2cf05d51e","tid":984633,"uid":19353,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"b269b472951547d80984bf4f9e5a1adbf796ff1d","tid":984633,"uid":11977,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"主管： 屌你老母唔預埋我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"主管真正不滿原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ef288af10272669d67c1af9e7b91c9d8cc8d8e","tid":984633,"uid":54181,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bab9ab260374d96187606a130a5f0961f3a1587","tid":984633,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92ef288af10272669d67c1af9e7b91c9d8cc8d8e","tid":984633,"uid":54181,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"他們仍然會保持聯繫，計劃從現在起一年的聚會，並通過電話和短信保持聯絡。"},{"pid":"1a586d593a5e3b682566c1d486f66799661ed44c","tid":984633,"uid":209663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b088b7426ba0b974d7adc9e7fa17590fa643f0","tid":984633,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":15,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"俾你中左3.5億 係咪第一時間買兇毆跛雞姦朗對腳?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"訓身買對阿變7億"},{"pid":"d192e896e379d5f0e84c34feae826e48ce12c0b9","tid":984633,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"好勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999a8a6e14697feed6e9f2f0b8965868d0b2ac7c","tid":984633,"uid":75193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"我睇新聞話有另外十一個無夾<br />\n日日係度呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以頂唔順一齊走"},{"pid":"31e552a2f0f784ed77b7ba080301da78b62a1c22","tid":984633,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:25:34.000Z","msg":"傻鳩主管 做埋果9個人既野喇<br />\n咁多野講"},{"pid":"4a74103936f48cdc500fbe0bb7d744a660b2e697","tid":984633,"uid":57462,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"中國人：買果個夾帶私逃"},{"pid":"2e914e4835d84cf3f0e385cac203b90031192252","tid":984633,"uid":32403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"21歲個個人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 埋左班廢老堆 輕鬆搞掂"},{"pid":"dffc5be375a925ca626e8a9f551bc911fd1854fe","tid":984633,"uid":32403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a74103936f48cdc500fbe0bb7d744a660b2e697","tid":984633,"uid":57462,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"中國人：買果個夾帶私逃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係根本無派彩"},{"pid":"2e508c7de90d3ca46ebbc9c3b2689fc23c9fa753","tid":984633,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"想 我都好想好似中左頭獎"},{"pid":"02bd230d33489c68941f78af308e2a4d1e4498ab","tid":984633,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:31:50.